description:
This course is about the basics to graphic design and logo design. In this course, you will learn the basic components to building a logo while exercising your knowledge through sketching exercises and at the end of this course - learn to design a brand mark logo.

Included in this course, is the entire second section of a full course I will be launching on Mastering Logo Design. That course contains full knowledge on graphic design, logo design, freelancing and will all be available to you at a discount when you join this course.

So are you ready to take your graphic design skills to the next level? Than start by joining this free course on Graphic Design and Logo Design.

You'll be happy you did.
title: Logo Design Complete Guide - Preview
